{"id":1565,"category_slug":"toeic","category_name":"TOEIC Listening","position":363,"title":"Conversation 183","subtitle":"Booking Theater Tickets Request","level":"B1","parts":15,"url":"https://dailydictation.com/exercises/toeic/conversation-183.1565/listen-and-type","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-183-2024-09-14-18-36-10/0-conversation-183.mp3","transcript":"Hello, I'm a guest in room 3110.\nI'd like to know if there are any tickets available for The Lion King this evening.\nCertainly.\nThey have quite a few orchestra seats left,\nwhich range from $80 to $220 each.\nI would recommend seats in the center orchestra.\nThey are arguably the best in the theater.\nUh, remind me again...\nOrchestra seats are the seats on the ground floor, right?\nI'd like two seats not too close to the stage.\nHow much are they?\nRight, two seats in Row Q will be $240, sir.\nThe show starts at 8 pm.\nI'll have your tickets here at the desk by 4 pm.\nThank you very much. I appreciate it.","youtube_video_id":"","details_cached_at":"2026-06-15T21:02:56","challenges":[{"position":1,"content":"Hello, I'm a guest in room 3110.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-183-2024-09-14-18-36-10/1.mp3","time_start":0.28,"time_end":3.74},{"position":2,"content":"I'd like to know if there are any tickets available for The Lion King this evening.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-183-2024-09-14-18-36-10/2.mp3","time_start":3.74,"time_end":8.06},{"position":3,"content":"Certainly.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-183-2024-09-14-18-36-10/3.mp3","time_start":8.06,"time_end":9.0},{"position":4,"content":"They have quite a few orchestra seats left,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-183-2024-09-14-18-36-10/4.mp3","time_start":9.0,"time_end":11.34},{"position":5,"content":"which range from $80 to $220 each.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-183-2024-09-14-18-36-10/5.mp3","time_start":11.34,"time_end":15.37},{"position":6,"content":"I would recommend seats in the center orchestra.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-183-2024-09-14-18-36-10/6.mp3","time_start":15.37,"time_end":18.24},{"position":7,"content":"They are arguably the best in the theater.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-183-2024-09-14-18-36-10/7.mp3","time_start":18.24,"time_end":20.83},{"position":8,"content":"Uh, remind me again...","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-183-2024-09-14-18-36-10/8.mp3","time_start":20.83,"time_end":23.01},{"position":9,"content":"Orchestra seats are the seats on the ground floor, right?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-183-2024-09-14-18-36-10/9.mp3","time_start":23.01,"time_end":26.23},{"position":10,"content":"I'd like two seats not too close to the stage.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-183-2024-09-14-18-36-10/10.mp3","time_start":26.23,"time_end":29.44},{"position":11,"content":"How much are they?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-183-2024-09-14-18-36-10/11.mp3","time_start":29.44,"time_end":30.5},{"position":12,"content":"Right, two seats in Row Q will be $240, sir.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-183-2024-09-14-18-36-10/12.mp3","time_start":30.5,"time_end":34.95},{"position":13,"content":"The show starts at 8 pm.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-183-2024-09-14-18-36-10/13.mp3","time_start":34.95,"time_end":36.67},{"position":14,"content":"I'll have your tickets here at the desk by 4 pm.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-183-2024-09-14-18-36-10/14.mp3","time_start":36.67,"time_end":39.41},{"position":15,"content":"Thank you very much. I appreciate it.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-183-2024-09-14-18-36-10/15.mp3","time_start":39.41,"time_end":42.2}]}